translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,11,"Ngempela labo abeze namanga bayiqembu eliphuma phakathi kwenu ningakuthathi ngokuthi kuyinto embi kunina, kepha kona kungcono kunina kubona bonke abantu phakathi kwabo yilokho akusebenzele okuyisono. Futhi lowo phakathi kwabo onengxenye enkulu kukona okwakhe isijeziso esikhulu"
  24,12,"Kungani uma senikuzwile lokho abakholwayo besilisa nabesifazane bangabacabangeli okuhle abantu babo futhi bathi, “lokhu kungamanga acacile yini na?”"
  24,13,Kungani bengalethanga kuyena ofakazi abane na? Ngakho-ke uma bengabalethi ofakazi kusho ukuthi bona kuMvelinqang bangabaqambi bamanga
  24,14,Futhi ukube babungekho ububele bukaMvelinqangi phezu kwenu nomusa wakhe kulomhlaba nasempilweni ezayo ngempela isijeziso esikhulu sasizonithinta ngenxa yalokho enikushilo
  24,15,Khumbula ngenkathi nikwemukela ngezilimi zenu futhi nikhuluma ngemilomo yenu lokho eningenalwazi ngakho nikuthatha njengento elula kulapho kuMvelinqangi kuyinto enkulu
  24,16,"Futhi kwenziwa yini ngenkathi nikuzwa nithi “Akusifanele ukuthi singakhuluma ngalokhu, udumo lungolwakho (Mvelinqangi) lokhu kuyisihlebo esikhulu”"
  24,17,UMvelinqangi uyaniyala ngokuthi ningaphindeli kokufana nako uma kungukuthi nina ningamakholwa
  24,18,"FuthiuMvelinqangiuyanicaciselaamavesi, futhiuMvelinqangi uyazi unobuhlakani"
  24,19,Ngempela labo abathanda ukudlulisela okubi kulabo abakholwayo okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu kulomhlaba nasempilweni ezayo futhi uMvelinqangi uyazi nina anazi
  24,20,"Futhi ukube babungekho ububele bukaMvelinqangi phezu kwenu kanye nomusa wakhe, futhi uMvelinqangi umnene unesihawu"